{"word":"G1357 - διόρθωσις - diórthōsis - dee-or'-tho-sis - Reformation","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διόρθωσις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>diórthōsis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>dee-or'-tho-sis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Reformation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சீர்திருத்தம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"correction.amendment, reform"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos'/3717\">G3717</a>, meaning to <i>straighten thoroughly</i>; <i>rectification</i>, that is, (specifically) the Messianic restoration: - reformation."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1357 - διόρθωσις - diórthōsis - dee-or'-tho-sis/1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G1882 - ἐπανόρθωσις - epanórthōsis - ep-an-or'-tho-sis/1882\">G1882</a>, <a href=\"#/G3716 - ὀρθοποδέω - orthopodéō - or-thop-od-eh'-o/3716\">G3716</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos'/3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718 - ὀρθοτομέω - orthotoméō - or-thot-om-eh'-o/3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719 - ὀρθρίζω - orthrízō - or-thrid'-zo/3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720 - ὀρθρινός - orthrinós - or-thrin-os'/3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721 - ὄρθριος - órthrios - or'-three-os/3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722 - ὄρθρος - órthros - or'-thros/3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723 - ὀρθῶς - orthōs - or-thoce'/3723\">G3723</a>"}]}